Claude.ai — composer is a ProseMirror contenteditable with a stable data-testid.

## Typing
- Prefer `[data-testid="chat-input"]` over class-based selectors (classes change on deploy).
- form_input does NOT work. Use execCommand:
  const ed = document.querySelector('[data-testid="chat-input"]');
  ed.focus();
  document.execCommand('insertText', false, 'your prompt here');
- Verify text appeared before sending.

## Auth
- Everything requires sign-in (OIDC). Fresh browser fingerprints sometimes get a Cloudflare Turnstile challenge on the first visit — wait for it to clear.

## Reading a streaming response
- Same signal as chatgpt: the 'Stop' button disappearing marks turn-complete. Read only after that.
- Artifacts (code blocks, documents) render in a right-hand panel. To read artifact contents, target the panel, not the message bubble.

## Navigation
- Conversation: claude.ai/chat/{uuid}
- Project: claude.ai/project/{uuid}
- Share: claude.ai/share/{uuid}
